libvsgpt is a library to access the GUID Partition Table (GPT) volume system format.

Project information:

* Status: experimental
* Licence: LGPL-3.0-or-later

For more information see:

* Project documentation: https://github.com/libyal/libvsgpt/wiki/Home
* How to build from source: https://github.com/libyal/libvsgpt/wiki/Building

